To update a table in flash memory of STM32L072, you need to follow a few steps. Below is the general procedure to update flash memory on STM32L072:

1. First, you need to define your table and its structure in the code.

   For example, you could define a table as an array of structures:

   ```
   typedef struct
   {
     uint8_t variable1;
     uint16_t variable2;
